M|prd-development|**Skill type:** Workflow
M|prd-development|**Suggested filename:** `prd-dev.md`
M|prd-development|**Suggested placement:** `/skills/workflows/`
M|prd-development|**Dependencies:** Orchestrates 8+ component and interactive skills across 8 phases